## 7. Key Data Structures

### BorrowError (returned as structured error, not a panic)
```rust
pub struct BorrowError {
    pub path: PathBuf,
    pub holder: SessionInfo,   // who holds the write lock
    pub acquired_at: SystemTime,
    pub ttl: Option<Duration>,
}

pub struct SessionInfo {
    pub session_id: Uuid,
    pub task_id: String,
    pub agent_label: Option<String>,
}
```

### DeltaManifest
```rust
pub struct DeltaManifest {
    pub base_commit: git2::Oid,    // or gix ObjectId
    pub writes:   HashMap<PathBuf, BlobHash>,   // path → content hash
    pub deletes:  HashSet<PathBuf>,
    pub renames:  Vec<(PathBuf, PathBuf)>,       // (from, to)
}
```

### SessionRecord (SQLite row mapped to Rust)
```rust
pub struct Session {
    pub id:           Uuid,
    pub task_id:      String,
    pub agent_label:  Option<String>,
    pub base_commit:  String,        // git OID hex
    pub created_at:   DateTime<Utc>,
    pub status:       SessionStatus,
    pub mount_path:   PathBuf,
    pub branch_name:  Option<String>,
}

pub enum SessionStatus { Active, Committed, Aborted, Stale }
```


